  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4125e41507de8ad40baa75593ae6fe1d, type: 3}
  m_Name: 01_Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  optionText: Ready to start?
  nextScene: 0
  sequence:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 62d8f7f1bc7a69c468148ba536fbd252, type: 2}
  dialogue:
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 1
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 1
    text: 'The year was 2021.

      The world was as it always was. '
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Humans going about their lives as they always have.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: In the late 2010s, a certain company became the envy of the business world.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Despite its sudden appearance on the world stage, this company grew to
      become one of the highest - if not the highest - grossing companies based on
      revenue in record time.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: It's name...
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a4e56ace704e6d145848b5bc453db6d3, type: 3}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: The Chaldea Security Organization.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: With a focus on pharmaceuticals and technology, the Chaldea Security Organization,
      or "Chaldea" for short, developed many breakthroughs for medicine, AI, and
      computing throughout its history.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: But it was not all smooth sailing, however. Some spoke out against Chaldea's
      wealth and influence.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: And rumors claiming involvement with PMCs and human experimentation surrounded
      the company.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Of course, all spokespeople representing the company denied allegations.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: '...Now you. John Wingard.

      You were one of many humans living in
      the 21st century.'
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: You weren't sure when it began - if it was there all along or if you only
      just started noticing it, but Chaldea was hiring.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: No info on the position looking to be filled was given, the company only
      stating they sought "talented young individuals seeking to change the world".
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: '"Did you see that Chaldea is hiring?"

      "Yeah, I wonder what they''re
      planning on doing this time!"

      "I bet it''s something amazing!"'
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: '"...Hey, *you* should apply!"'
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: 'The people in your life spoke of this hiring ad.

      There were promoted
      posts on your social media feed.

      Even flyers in your mailbox.'
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: It was like there was no subtlety - it was as if the world itself was pushing
      you to do this.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: For whatever reason, you decided there was no harm in applying. The day
      after, a representative of the company got in touch.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: The director of Chaldea themselves wished to speak with you personally;
      the company offering to pay for your trip.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: '1st class.

      All expenses paid.'
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 1
    text: 'And so, you packed your belongings - just the necessities.

      You
      were picked up by a man-in-black, and driven to the airport in a black SUV
      with tinted windows.'
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1516e108f2f45fb4cb273f6a447430eb, type: 3}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: You were flown to Monument City, a newly founded city along the north-west
      United States and Canadian border.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Like before, you were driven to the company HQ in a black SUV and escorted
      by more men-in-black.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: The headquarters of the Chaldea Security Organization was an enormous glass
      pyramid situated in the center of the city.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Surrounding the building were guards in kevlar, armed with military-grade
      weapons.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Once inside, you were greeted by businessmen and women, all on their phones
      or heading somewhere. You also spotted people in labcoats throughout the lobby.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Following your escorts, you were led deeper into the building.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Strange, you thought. Rather than heading upwards, where you would expect
      the executives' offices to be, you were all heading downwards.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: In the deepest part of the building, there was an industrial elevator,
      large enough to fit some serious machinery.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 1
    text: One of the escorts pressed on the control panel, and the elevator begun
      heading downwards.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: 'It was a quiet ride, save for the hum of the lift''s machinery.

      The
      elevator had no walls, just a waist-high fence. You were surrounded by solid
      rock as the lift descended.'
  - actor: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f01954c4a89cc0d41ae4823d2744271a, type: 2}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: '"So... What position is it that you''re looking to fill?"'
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: '"I''m afraid that''s not something we were allowed to know," one of the
      men-in-black replied.

      The ride continued in silence.'
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: Finally, the ride came to a stop, and you were greeted by an enormous door
      marked with Chaldea's logo. It was a door meant for a nuclear bunker, not a
      business.
  - actor: {fileID: 0}
    Narrator: 1
    PortraitPosition: 0
    layer: 0
    ErasePortraits: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    FadeBGIn: 0
    EraseBG: 0
    text: You and your escorts boarded the elevator. One of the men-in-black pressed
      his earpiece and spoke, and the bunker door opened with a heavy grinding sound.
